creator: Arthur M. Winfield
description:
LibriVox recording of The Rover Boys In The Mountains by Arthur M. Winfield.
Read in English by VfkaBT
Another rousing tale of the Brothers Rover, set directly after their adventure in the Great Lakes, detailing yet another encounter with the dastardly Dan Baxter! - Summary by Matt Pierard
For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording.

For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org.
